root: ^Well, I'll be damned. How'd you manage to do that?
^I honestly have no idea. I remember dying, being surrounded by demons, and then crawling out of that grave. But here I am, alive and kicking.
^Shouldn't you be long dead fighting demons somewhere in the world? That's what I heard, at least.
^Actually, I still have that book that Annika gave me. And look, it's even glowing!
^(smirking) Well, well, well. That book might be the reason for all of this. You should open it and see what it says.
